Design Highlights of WQ809

  1. Sinking rock switch design is applied, which can prevent lighting triggered by accidental touch during transportation and avoid consequential combustion and explosion. 
  2. Lithium battery is applied, with significant characteristics as small, light, and environment-friendly. 
  3. Charging circuit has self-protection function, preventing the fixture from over charge. 
  4. Small volume and light weight, easy to carry.

There is battery indicator on LCD display screen. Please recharge in time when battery meter shows one bar of power left. Please disconnect the power after keeping recharge half an hour when indicator displays full power (five bars of power).
